data.description: SELLER GIVING BUYER $8000 CREDIT AT CLOSING FOR BUYDOWN OR CLOSING COSTS! Come see this 3/2 POOL HOME! As you step inside, you'll find yourself in a open living room that boasts a fireplace. To your left, there's a formal dining area, providing a perfect space for gatherings. The kitchen features expansive granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an additional breakfast nook. The master suite offers a standup shower, a luxurious soaker tub, a dual vanity for added convenience, and a walk-in closet. This home's layout includes a split floor plan, w/ the remaining bedrooms having ample space for family members or guests. Head out back to relax in your inground pool that is surrounded by a fully fenced backyard.
